    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1856-01-19T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1856-01-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="169" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d169">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Cushing</persName>,
                                    Attorney-General, to Mr. <persName type="to">McKeon</persName>,
                                    district attorney.</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Attorney-General’s
                                    Office</hi>
                    </placeName>,<lb/>
                    <date calendar="gregorian" when="1856-01-19">
                        <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 19,
                                1856</date>.</dateline>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the
                                receipt of your communication of the 16th instant, in relation to
                                the retention of the revenue-cutter Washington at the port of New
                                York, and have submitted the same to the Secretary of the Treasury.
                                I am informed by him that he has countermanded the orders requiring
                                the Washington to leave New York on a cruise, and directed her to
                                remain there.</p>
                <p>I am, very respectfully,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>C. CUSHING.</item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">John McKeon</hi>,<lb/>
                                <hi rend="italic">United States District
                                            Attorney.</hi>
                            </item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
